snippet.title: RULING THE SCHOOL ??? -  new io game schoolbreak.io - 42nd impressions
snippet.description:
sup my dude-os, Tyrant here with our 0 sub special video.

today we're playing schoolbreak.io - which's a cool game that just came out, you play as student trying to make the biggest mess at school OR as a teacher trying to put those kids in their place: detention - so yeah, we're a bit lucky that their place was somewhere they can't do any more pranks.

riddle me this:
there is one person writing this, and one person reading this - one of them I know nothing of, and the other one may or may not write a deceiving paragraph right after this one

also important to say that I 100% do not work for schoolbreak.io, pinky-swear - I totally didn't make this video just to get some mediocre gameplay footage out there so you can see it and go play it, and I totally won't get a raise if thirty million people play it.

the chest thing did legit freak me out though, we gotta fix that

cheers, cya
